  "detailed_description": "<strong>Over 90 Single Player Levels</strong><br>Fill-It has increasingly challenging levels and crazy evil new enemies will come at you from all directions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/c95a58b8116dce041e615c0175ffcff2.poster.avif?t=1654343610\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/c95a58b8116dce041e615c0175ffcff2.webm?t=1654343610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/c95a58b8116dce041e615c0175ffcff2.mp4?t=1654343610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Couch Multiplayer Madness</strong><br>Destroy your friends in lightning-fast matches of up to four players! Remember, it’s just a game, so don’t hold a grudge!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/391cd6b164bababad039e7497cae668f.poster.avif?t=1654343610\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/391cd6b164bababad039e7497cae668f.webm?t=1654343610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/391cd6b164bababad039e7497cae668f.mp4?t=1654343610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Team Up</strong><br>Happiness is to be shared. Beat your enemies together with a friend, in over 40 Local Co-Op challenging levels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1446540/extras/1d7efb702c2f54a33468501774a87425.poster.avif?t=1654343610\" width=600 